  Run   Level Mode          Action
  ---   ----------          ------
   0	Halt                Shuts down system
   1	Single-User Mode    Does not configure network interfaces,
                            start daemons, or allow non-root logins.
   2    Multi-User Mode     Does not configure network interfaces or start
                            daemons.
   3    Multi-User Mode     Starts the system normally.
        with Networking
   4    Undefined           Not used/User-definable
   5    X11                 As runlevel 3 + display manager(X)
   6    Reboot              Reboots the system